H. No. 2443 / 55 OG No. 37, 7884 (September 14, 1959)

[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 2499, June 21, 1959 ]

AN ACT CREATING CERTAIN BARRIOS IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF PALOMPON, PROVINCE OF LEYTE.

Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:

SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Palompon, Province of Leyte, are converted into barrios thereof, as follows:

The sitio of Caduhaan to be known as the barrio of Caduhaan;

The sitio of Cambakbak to be known as the barrio of Cambakbak;

The sitio of San Guillermo to be known as the barrio of San Guillermo;

The sitio of Lu-uk to be known as the barrio of San Isidro;

The sitio of Lat-osan to be known as the barrio of Lat-osan;

The sitio of San Joaquin to be known as the barrio of San Joaquin; and

The sitio of Cangmuya to be known as the barrio of Cangmuya.

SEC 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without executive approval, June 21, 1959.
